Also I would drop graves to B tier, because while he clears well, he only offers damage. and a lot of your lanes are not going to bring gank assist making him a lot worse for solo queue than in a team environment, where they will actually play champs like maokai or naut top.
Kindred I don't feel is B tier worthy, but I know some people do find success on her still (feel she is weaker than udyr though who you have in C tier)
And you can't have lee in S tier without having Ivern up there, seriously Ivern is so incredibly strong right now it is insane

I feel Xin is A tier worthy, even though a lot of people would disagree, simply because his early pressure allows him to compete with the S-tiers in a game and not be worthless, not because he outclasses the others in A-B Tier
And malphite is only A tier because of the best jg's being AD, and he does well vs the meta champs/comps

